Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.name: -didReceiveSampleBuffer:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.abstract: Called whenever a MiSnapFacialCaptureCamera instance outputs a new video frame (CMSampleBufferRef)

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.name: -didDropSampleBuffer:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.abstract: Delegates receive this message whenever a video frame is dropped. This method is called once for each dropped frame. The CMSampleBuffer object passed to this delegate method will contain metadata about the dropped video frame, such as its duration and presentation time stamp, but will contain no actual video data.

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.name: -didFinishConfiguringSession
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.abstract: Camera configuration must be done before final UX configuration to allow a smooth transition to the video presentation.

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.name: -didDecodeBarcode:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.abstract: Delegates receive this message whenever a PDF417 Data is decoded. This method is called once for each frame where a barcode is decoded. The NSString object passed to this delegate method will contain PDF417 Data.

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.name: -didFinishRecordingVideo:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureCameraDeleg.abstract: Delegates receive this message whenever a video is recorded. The NSData object passed to this delegate method contains recorded video.

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerError:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback after analysis of each frame that doesn’t pass image quality analysis checks

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerSuccess:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback whenever a final frame was selected that meets environmental thresholds defined in MiSnapFacialCaptureParameters

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerCancelled:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback whenever a user cancels a session

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerManualOnly
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback when device supports Manual only frame selection (iOS < 12.0)

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerStartCountdown
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback when selectOnSmile parameter is to FALSE and countdownTime is greater than or equal to 1 (second).

Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.name: -miSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerLicenseStatus:
Protocols/MiSnapFacialCaptureAnalyzerDel.abstract: Delegates receive this callback only when license status is anything but valid
